name: Madonna
description: Justify your love in this super soft and slightly distressed 100% heavyweight cotton YBF tee featuring: custom Madonna artwork by YoungBrokenFamous, inside out construction, hand distressed  body, collar, sleeves and hem. Each T has been washed 4x and hand dyed a dirty faded teal. These shirts are one size (slightly oversized) for a true 1990's aesthetic.
